<idea-plugin>
    <id>com.github.mars05.crud-plugin</id>
    <name>Crud</name>
    <vendor url="https://github.com/mars05/crud-intellij-plugin" email="xiaoyucoder@163.com">mars05</vendor>
    <category>Code Tools</category>
    <description><![CDATA[
<div>
    <p>
    <a href="https://github.com/mars05/crud-intellij-plugin" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">GitHub</a>
     | <a href="https://crud-hub.top/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">Crud Hub</a>
      | <a href="https://crud-hub.top/docs/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">在线文档</a>
    </p>
    <img src="https://gitee.com/mars05_xy/static/raw/master/crud-hub/crud-plugin.png">
    <h1> Crud Plugin </h1>
    <div>
        <p> A plugin for code generation that helps you quickly generate code from different templates based on database table structures. </p>
        <p> Features: </p>
        <ul>
            <li> Project generation: Create a new project </li>
            <li> Code generation: Generate code based on table structure in existing project </li>
            <li> Multiple databases: Maintains database connections globally, including MySQL, PostgreSQL, and Oracle  </li>
            <li> DDL: Supports code generation from DDL </li>
            <li> Template import: Import templates on demand from template markets or using access token </li>
        </ul>
        <p> For more information about curd please visit: <a href="https://github.com/mars05/crud-intellij-plugin">GitHub</a></p>
    </div>
    <br/>
    <br/>
    <div>
        <p> 一个用于代码生成的插件，可以根据数据库表结构，帮助您从不同的模板快速生成相关代码。 </p>
        <p> 特性: </p>
        <ul>
            <li> 项目生成: 创建一个新的项目 </li>
            <li> 代码生成: 在已有项目中，根据表结构生成代码 </li>
            <li> 多数据库: 全局维护数据库连接，目前支持MySQL、PostgreSQL、Oracle </li>
            <li> DDL: 支持从DDL生成代码 </li>
            <li> 模板导入: 按需从模板市场或使用访问令牌导入模板 </li>
        </ul>
        <p> 有关增删改查的更多信息，请访问: <a href="https://github.com/mars05/crud-intellij-plugin">GitHub</a></p>
    </div>
</div>
    ]]></description>
    <change-notes><![CDATA[
        Change notes will be filled by gradle build
]]></change-notes>
    <!-- please see http://www.jetbrains.org/intellij/sdk/docs/basics/getting_started/plugin_compatibility.html
         on how to target different products -->
    <!-- uncomment to enable plugin in all products
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.lang</depends>
    -->
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.lang</depends>
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.platform</depends>
    <depends>com.intellij.modules.java</depends>

    <depends optional="true" config-file="maven-support.xml">org.jetbrains.idea.maven</depends>

    <idea-version since-build="173.0"/>
    <extensions defaultExtensionNs="com.intellij">
        <!-- Add your extensions here -->
        <moduleBuilder builderClass="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.wizard.CrudModuleBuilder"/>
        <applicationService serviceImplementation="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.setting.CrudSettings"/>

        <applicationService
                serviceImplementation="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.dao.mapper.ProjectTemplateMapper"/>
        <applicationService
                serviceImplementation="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.service.ProjectTemplateService"/>


        <applicationConfigurable parentId="tools"
                                 instance="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.setting.CrudConfigurable"
        />
        <applicationConfigurable parentId="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.setting.CrudConfigurable"
                                 instance="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.setting.TemplateImportConfigurable"
        />
        <applicationConfigurable parentId="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.setting.CrudConfigurable"
                                 instance="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.setting.MyTemplateConfigurable"
        />
    </extensions>

    <actions>
        <group id="CrudActionGroup" text="Crud"
               popup="true" icon="/icons/logo.png">
            <add-to-group group-id="ProjectViewPopupMenu" anchor="last"/>
        </group>
        <!-- Add your actions here -->
        <action class="com.github.mars05.crud.intellij.plugin.action.NewFileAction"
                id="crud.NewFileAction" description="CodeGenerate"
                icon="/icons/code.svg"
                text="代码生成">
            <add-to-group group-id="CrudActionGroup"/>
        </action>
    </actions>
</idea-plugin>